SUMMARY:JYCM Monthly Program: Feminism and the Climate Crisis
DESCRIPTION:Join JYCM for the March Monthly Program\nThe Jewish Youth Climate Movement is hosting monthly programs this semester\, March’s program is Feminism and the Climate Crisis \nRegisterEvent DetailsJoin the Jewish Youth Climate Movement to build community through bonding activities and learn about the intersections between feminism and climate change. This program is for teens exclusively!
URL:https://adamah.org/event/jycm-feminism-and-the-climate-crisis/
LOCATION:Zoom
CATEGORIES:JYCM
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Intro-to-the-Jewish-Climate-Leadership-Coalition-2.png
