LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T193005Z
UID:24452-1773759600-1773763200@adamah.org
SUMMARY:Fund Your Climate Future: Loans & Grants for Jewish Nonprofits
DESCRIPTION:3pm ET/12pm PT (60 minutes) \n\nTaking climate action can be both a morally and financially responsible decision\nWhat’s good for the planet is often good for your budget! Learn more at the webinar. \nRegisterEvent DetailsThe Jewish Climate Leadership Coalition offers FREE membership that unlocks exclusive resources\, like access to interest-free loans for energy efficiency and renewable energy projects\, plus regional grant programs specifically designed for Jewish nonprofits.  \nOur next funding application deadline is April 16\, 2026\, there’s still plenty of time to join the Coalition and secure the financial support your organization needs to make meaningful climate impact.
URL:https://adamah.org/event/webinar-fund-your-climate-future/
LOCATION:Virtual\, Zoom / Online
CATEGORIES:Coalition
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/laptop-setup-desk-stockcake.webp
END:VEVENT
