SUMMARY:Avodat Lev Hike - Palo Alto
DESCRIPTION:Registration is free. Donations are welcome. \nLet’s Get Together\, Outside!\nWe’re heading into the hills for a hike that’s part adventure\, part heart-opening\, part “wow\, look at that view.” Avodat Lev means service of the heart\, and this walk is an invitation to slow down\, breathe deeper\, and notice what’s alive around and within us. \nExpect good company\, open sky\, winding trails\, and moments of reflection tucked between footsteps. You can come solo\, with a friend\, with a partner\, with kids\, with anyone who loves being outside. \nJust bring your walking shoes and a little curiosity. \nRegisterEvent Details
URL:https://adamah.org/event/avodat-lev-hike-palo-alto/
LOCATION:Wunderlich County Park
CATEGORIES:San Francisco Bay Area
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Adamah-SF-Avodat-Lev-Hike-Palo-Alto.jpg
END:VEVENT
