SUMMARY:From Wheat to Matzah: Family Matzah Making
DESCRIPTION:Make Matzah with your family at Pearlstone!\nJoin us for a hands-on family journey from wheat kernels to matzah! We’ll gather to make matzah together – grinding and sifting wheat kernels by hand\, kneading the dough\, and baking fresh matzah over an open fire. \nRegisterEvent DetailsLearn how to make fresh matzah over an open fire on a saj. \nWe’ll eat together\, sing Passover songs\, and connect with this ancient practice as a community.
URL:https://adamah.org/event/family-matzah-making/
LOCATION:Pearlstone Retreat Center & Campus\, 5425 Mt. Gilead Rd\, Reisterstown\, MD\, 21136
CATEGORIES:Pearlstone,Pearlstone Education,Pesach
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/11868671473_e79f27e840_c.jpg
END:VEVENT
