SUMMARY:Energy Audits as a Starting Point
DESCRIPTION:12pm ET/9am PT  \n\n\n \nWondering where to start with climate action?\nIn this webinar\, we’ll demystify what an energy audit actually is\, help guide you to the appropriate type of audit for your organization. \nRegisterEvent DetailsAn energy audit is one of the smartest first steps\, and it generally pays for itself. An audit shows you exactly where your building is losing energy and money\, then gives you a clear roadmap for what to do about it. The best part? Many audits are available for free through state and utility programs\, and most recommendations are low-cost or no-cost changes that save you money right away.  \nIn this webinar\, we’ll demystify what an energy audit actually is\, help guide you to the appropriate type of audit for your organization\, and introduce a special group discount opportunity through Energy for Purpose. Energy audits take the guesswork out of climate action while saving you money.  \nThis program is produced as a part of the Jewish Climate Leadership Coalition\, learn more here. \nWith enough interest from Jewish organizations\, Adamah may be able to facilitate a group discount on professional energy audits from our partner\, Energy for Purpose. If your organization is interested in getting a discounted energy audit\, fill out this form to let us know
URL:https://adamah.org/event/energy-audits-2026/
LOCATION:Virtual\, Zoom / Online
CATEGORIES:Coalition
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://adamah.org/wp-content/uploads/MicrosoftTeams-image-1.png
END:VEVENT
