SUMMARY:2026 Jewish Climate Summit
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a warm\, in-person Earth Day Climate Summit\nbringing together members of the Jewish climate community for an evening of connection\, reflection\, and shared purpose. \nRegistration Coming Soon!Event DetailsThis hopeful and joyful event will focus on climate resilience\, spiritual grounding\, and the power of showing up better together — with food\, music\, art\, and dedicated time to meet and build relationships across organizations. Additional details and speakers will be added in the coming weeks.  
