SUMMARY:Commonpoint’s Multi-Building Energy Transformation - Climate Action in Practice
DESCRIPTION:Join Adamah NY\,\nCommonpoint\, and Rich Energy Solutions \nA real-world nonprofit case study on modernizing aging buildings through multi-building energy upgrades and Building Management Systems (BMS). \nRegisterEvent Details \nLearn how strategic planning\, integrated design\, staff training\, and funding pathways can improve comfort\, resilience\, and long-term cost control.  \nHear directly from partners who implemented this work and leave with a practical roadmap for your own organization. 
